              ', E'Unknown', E'Unknown', E'Possible base of a statue', '2014-08-05 17:15:00', NULL, E'two objects, 6-7-12\r\n\r\nShort description: rectangular travertine slab, broken in two. Possible base of a statue\r\nLocation: W of Via Appia, N of 331-334, on the slope of 338');
